<h1>The Term Tool</h1> 
 <p>
  The <b>Term</b> tool is used to add terms, including the <b>start date</b> and the <b>end date</b> of the term.
 </p>
 <h1>How to use the Term Tool</h1>
 <p>
  There are three boxes where you type:

  <ol>
   <li>The Title</li>
   <li>The Start date</li>
   <li>The End date</li>
  </ol>
The <b>Title</b> section is where you type in the title of the term.
<br/><br/>

The <b>Start date</b> section is where you type the date that the term started.<br/>
The button "..." next to the Start date box will type in the present date in the box
<br/><br/>

The <b>End date</b> section is where you type the date that the term ended.<br/>
The button "..." next to the End date box will type in the present date in the box

